cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper addresses the task of single image super resolution with the presence of image degradation, which is a fundamental task in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The proposed method uses a dual-branch convolutional neural network, which involves deep learning techniques, indicating that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on benchmark datasets, which suggests that it could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.GR (Graphics).
